Step to clean the Data 11

 Replace Values (This Step help us to clean the data because there are some steps the data is not clear)

(1) Click to State Column

(2) Click to Transform--->Replace Values

(3) In the Value to find box, type the value that we went to replace with another value.  In the Replace with box, type 

the value that we want to replace with

(4) Click OK
